flowchart TD
    VT[View tree - tagged DomNodes] --> RW[render_raster_view_tree walk]
    RW --> RC[rc_* painter render_painter.cpp]
    RC --> GW[PaintRecordTarget gateway]
    GW --> PL[PaintList - PaintIR semantic cmds]

    PL -->|paint_ir_lower_raster| DL[DisplayList - raster ops in ScratchArena]
    PL -->|paint_ir_lower_svg| SVGOUT[SVG fragment StrBuf]

    subgraph Backends [RenderBackend vtable seam]
        RASTER[Raster - full-node overrides]
        SVGB[SVG backend render_svg.cpp]
        PDFB[PDF backend render_pdf.cpp]
    end

    RC -.through.-> RASTER
    SVGB -->|consumes PaintIR| PL
    PDFB -->|consumes PaintIR| PL

    DL --> CAP[retained_dl_cache_capture]
    CAP --> CACHE[RetainedDisplayList cache]
    DL --> REPLAY1[dl_replay single thread]
    DL --> REPLAYN[dl_replay_tile x N parallel]
    CACHE -.reuse clean fragments.-> DL
    REPLAY1 --> PIX[surface pixels via rdt_*]
    REPLAYN --> PIX
